    "7210614": {
        "Desc": "Head over to the designated area recorded in the notebook",
        "Step": "The key to descending the well is \"a broken house across the gully on the east side of the village.\" You're getting closer to the heart of this mystery.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "What can I do for you, youngster?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You are...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "My name is Konda Densuke, and I am the village chief."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "From the way you dress, you must be an outsi— I mean, outlander, right? It's been a long time since an outlander has come to the village."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "How can I help you? Need a place to rest your feet? Or do you need help to find your way up the mountain?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm looking for a place to rest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I want to go up the mountain."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No! We're here to ask about the secret of Konda Village!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...Oh boy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "Secret? Konda Village doesn't have any secrets."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "Although the economy isn't good these days, all the taxes that should be paid to the police station are paid regularly, regardless."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "There are only a few families in our village, all with a long history. And we know each other's roots. How could we have any secrets?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Calm down a little..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "Konda Village is simple and peaceful. There are no secrets here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "If you're looking for secrets, why don't you just go to the Grand Narukami Shrine and learn the secrets of deciphering fortune slips? Or how about you go to Chinju Forest and see if you can hear the \"tanuki-bayashi,\" huh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "Phew... Sorry, I might have overreacted."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "Konda Village is a peaceful place. Youngster, are you sure you don't have the wrong village?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Konda Densuke",
                    "T": "If you don't believe me, <color=#00E1FFFF>you can look around yourself</color>. I, Konda Densuke, will not stand in your way."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
