    "7210701": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "A fox statue... Yup, it's the same as the one in Konda Village!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But Paimon doesn't see a ward in it... or has the ward been hidden?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh, it's some troublesome <color=#00E1FFFF>secret</color> again, isn't it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We're a pretty good combination..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehehe, right? The village chief told us everything."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I sure hope that isn't the case..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait! There's some writing here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "<color=#00E1FFFF>\"The ward has been sealed within by sacred words.\"</color>"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm, what does that mean? There's some more writing here as well..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Although I hope the seal will never be broken, and although you have now been missing for many years... If the seal must be broken and the Cleansing Ritual conducted, I hope that you shall be the one to break it.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"The third line of the sacred words is something you often used to say in the past.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't get it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is there anything else?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let Paimon see... \"But if the one to undo the seal is my successor, then there is one extra step you must go through.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"There are four great spirits, and three spokes in the Mitsudomoe. I have placed <color=#00E1FFFF>three shikigami</color> here as guardians. <color=#00E1FFFF>Only when they are all gathered here in one place</color> can you proceed.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"I wouldn't call this layer of security all that useful, but it should still serve to fend off some petty thieves.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Eh!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What is it, Paimon?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then we have to find a solution!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Otherwise, we'd be no better than \"petty thieves\"!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
