    "7210004": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "Ah. We meet again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "Although it is a pity that we are unable to meet where the sun shines for now, the light from the Thunder Sakura, which symbolizes the divine, and the light from your aura are enough to illuminate this space. If there is anything I can help you with, please let me know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About the other barriers..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "Apart from Chinju Forest, there is a barrier in a place called Araumi."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "Finally, there is a pit on a beach northeast of the Kamisato residence's courtyard. That is where you will find the final barrier."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I couldn't find the ward..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "In the past, the ward was guarded by the Sky Kitsune. But after everything changed, the Sky and Earth Kitsune eventually refused to show up, instead sleeping and waiting for her return."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "If you want to find the ward, look for the Sky Kitsune around the seal... that should be a special fox statue. If you're having difficulties, try to find the Earth Kitsune nearby, or use that Lens to see if there are any clues."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About the Memento Lens..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "I'm afraid I don't know much more about this than you. Apart from the Hiiragi Clan's squandering of their divine gift, that is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "There are many sleeping Earth Kitsune in Narukami Island. What you may see before you, though, is most likely to be a small, special fox statue."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "In the past, though they were weak in strength, they valued loyalty. If you look at them through the Memento Lens, you should be able to see some scenes from the past."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Goodbye."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "\"Our hearts drift with the clouds...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hanachirusato",
                    "T": "If there is anything I can help you with, please do not hesitate to let me know."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
