        "Desc": "Find the little tanuki",
        "Step": "The ward of the Chinju Forest is indeed in the hands of bake-danuki Ioroi, and Ioroi is willing to give it up. But he will only do so after you have found and played with the three little bake-danuki: Shousei, Gyoubu Koban, and Kichiboushi...",
